content:
Add a Custom Bot User

By default, each bot is assigned to the Basic Chatbot User. If you want a bot to use features or objects that require additional permissions, assign it to a custom user.

To build and manage Einstein Bots:
 
Customize Application
OR
Modify Metadata
OR
Manage Bots

To assign a Custom Chatbot User: 
Manage Users

The bot performs actions based on the user itâ€™s assigned to. Before you assign a custom user to your bot, ensure that the user has access to features like objects, Visualforce pages, and Apex classes.

In the Bot Builder menu, click Overview.
Click Edit under Bot User and select Custom Chatbot User.
Select a user and save your changes.
title: Service Cloud Einstein Bots: Adding a Custom Bot User
